Fast Movement (Ex): Land base speed +10 feet, medium armor or medium load max

Illiterate

Rage (ex): +4 Str / Con +2 morale to will, -2 AC. 1 / day + 1/4 levels. 3 + Con Mod rounds. Become fatigued at the end
Uncanny Dodge (ex): Retain dex bonus to AC when flat-footed or against invisible foes. Does not apply if imobilized
Trap Sense (ex): Dodge bonus to AC and untyped bonus to Reflex. + 1/3 Levels
Improved Uncanny Dodge (ex): Cannot be flanked. Can only be sneak attacked by someone with (levels + 4) rogue levels
Damage Reduction (ex): DR (1 + (level - 7)/3)
Greater Rage (ex): Bonuses increase to +6 Str / Con and +3 Morale bonus to Will
Indomitable Will (Ex): During rage, an additional +4 to Will against enchantment.
Tireless Rage (Ex): no longer become fatigued at the end of rage
Mighty Rage (ex): Rage bonuses increase to +8 to Str / Con and +4 morale bonus to will

Bardic Knowledge (ex): (level + int mod) for miscellaneous knowledge.

Bardic Music: (level) times / day.
Countersong (Su): Perform 3 ranks miniumum. use perform check in place of saves against sound dependent abilities for creatures within 30' for up to 10 rounds.
Fasciante (Sp): Perform rank 3 minumum. Fascinate 1 + ((level-1)/3) creatures within 90'. Will save = perform check. 24 hr lockout. Effect last 1 round / bard level
Inspire Courage (Su): Effect lasts for duration + 5 rounds. +1 morale bonus against charm and fear, +1 morale to attacks and damage roles. increases at 8 and every 6 after. Mind-affecting
Inspire Competence (Su): Perform 6 ranks min. +2 competence to an ally within 30' on a particular skill. Duration, concentration, up to 2 minutes.
Suggestion (Sp): On a fascinated target, can use suggestion, as the spell. Save is 10+ 1/2 bard level + Cha mod. Enchantment (Compulsion), Mind-affecting, Language dependent.

Inspire Greatness (Su): Perform 12 ranks minimum. Self or a single ally, +1 additional target per 3 levels. Lasts for sound duration +5 rounds. grants 2 HD (d10s), +2 competence on attack rolls, +1 competence on Fort saves. Mind-affecting.
Song of Freedom (Sp): Perform 15 ranks minimum. As break enchament, cl = bard level. Requires 1 minute of uninterrupted concentration and music. 1 target within 30'. Can't use on self.
Inspire Heroics (Su): Perform 18 ranks minimum. Self or one ally, +1 target per additional 3 levels. +4 morale on saves, and +4 dodge to AC. Lasts for song duration + 5 rounds.
Mass Suggestion (Sp): As suggestion above, but applies to any number of fascinated creatures.

Aura (Ex): Has an aura of the appropriate alignment and strength.

Turn or Rebuke Undead (Su): Turn 3 + Cha mod times / day

Bonus Languages: May choose from Celestial, Abyssal, and Infernal, in additional to choices granted by race

Animal Companion (Ex): 0+2(level/3) HD 0+2(level/3) NA 0+(level/3) Str/Dex 1+(level/3) Tricks. Link, share spells.

Nature Sense (Ex): +2 on Knowledge (Nature) and Survival checks.

Wild Empathy (Ex): As Diplomacy, on animals. 1d20 + level + cha mod
Woodland Stride (Ex): Ignore penalties from nature undergrowth
Trackless Step (Ex): Leave no trail in natural surroundings, unless you wish to.
Resist Nature's Lure (Ex): +4 bonus on saves against spell-like abilities of fey
Wild Shape (Su): Small or medium animal. As polymorph, except 1 hour / druid level. Standard action. 1 / day + 1 at 6, 7, 10, 14, 18.
Wild Shape (Large) (Ex): May now Wild Shape into Large animals
Venom Immunity (Ex): Gain immunity to all posions
Wild Shape (Tiny) (Ex): May now Wild Shape into Tiny animals
Wild Shape (Plant) (Ex): May now Wild Shape into Plant creatures in addition to Animals
A Thousand Faces (Su): May change appearance at will, as the Alter Self spell, but only in normal form

Timeless Body (Ex): No penalties from aging from this point forward. Bonuses still accrue. Death from old age still occurs.

Wild Shape (Huge) (Ex): May Wild Shape into Huge forms as well
Wild Shape (Elemental) (Ex): May Wild Shape into a Small, Medium, or Large Air, Earth, Fire, or Water elemental. 1 + 1 / 2 additional druid levels.
Wild Shape (Huge Elemental) (Ex): May now Wild Shape into Huge Elementals

Aura of Good (Ex): As a clerics

Detect Evil (Sp): At will, as the spell. CL = paladin level

Smite Evil (Su): 1 + 1/5 levels / day. + Cha mod to attack roll, and + paladin level to damage roll against evil target.

Code of Conduct: Must be lawful good, respect authority, act with honor, help those in need, and punish those who harm or threaten innocents.

Associates: Must never knowingly associate with evil characters, continue association with someone who offends their moral code, and only accept henchmen, followers, or cohorts who are lawful good.

Divine Grace (Su): + Cha mod to all saves

Lay on Hands (Su): Level x Cha mod points per day.

Aura of Courage (Su): Immune to fear, allies with 10' get +4 morale against fear.
Divine Health (Ex): Immune to all diseases, including supernatural and magical diseases
Turn Undead (Su): 3 + cha mod /day, as cleric of paladin level - 3
Special Mount (Sp):
Remove Disease (Sp): As the spell, 1 + 1/3 additional levels / week . CL = paladin level.
